<title>nhtf lsydnạ fạdynạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (nhtf lsydnạ fạdynạ .. wmlknạ ạlgẖạly yswʿ
 bfrḥ nrfʿ ạ̉gẖạnynạ .. wʿlmnạ kmạn mrfwʿ)2
 ạlqrạr- (qdws ạlbạr wạ̹lh jbạr)2
 2- (ndws bʿz wḥryẗ .. ʿly kl qwy̱ ạlsẖyṭạn
 slṭạn wfyh ạlbnwyẗ .. bạlnʿmẗ wbạlạ̹ymạn)2
 3- (qạỷdnạ ḍạmn mwạʿydh .. mn nṣr lạ̹ntṣạr
 nʿly rạyẗ tmjydh .. bṣlyb ạlạ̹ftkẖạr)2
 4- (wmʿdyyn ạlbryẗ .. bạlfrḥ wbạlạ̉nạsẖyd
 whnạk fy nwr ạlạ̉bdyẗ .. ạ̉ʿyạdnạ tkwn tmjyd)2</lyrics>
